{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)UIControl","text":"UIControl"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"control"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"mapView","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The map view containing the specified annotation.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"annotation","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation whose accessory view was tapped."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"control","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The control that was tapped."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In a standard callout view, accessory views contain custom content and are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"positioned on either side of the annotation title text. If an accessory view","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"you specify is a descendant of the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIControl"},{"text":" class, the map view calls this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method as a convenience whenever the user taps your view. You can use this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method to respond to taps and perform any actions associated with that control.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"For example, if your control displays additional information about the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation, you could use this method to present a modal panel with that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If your custom accessory views are not descendants of the ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" class,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the map view does not call this method. If the annotation has a custom callout","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view via the ","type":"text"},{"code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method, you can specify the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"custom accessory views using the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"leftAccessoryView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"rightAccessoryView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" properties.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Related-examples","text":"Related examples","level":4,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to trigger an action when the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"standard callout bubble’s accessory control is tapped."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metada